e news|url=https://www.sanspo.com/geino/news/20190323/geo19032305040007-n1.html|title=\u30ca\u30ab\u30df\u30fc\u3001\u53e4\u5de3\u30d5\u30b8\u3067\u51fa\u7523\u5f8c\u521d\u30ec\u30ae\u30e5\u30e9\u30fc\uff01\u4e43\u6728\u5742\u306b\u300c\u5929\u4f7f\u3067\u3059\u306d\u300d|newspaper=Sankei Sports|date=2019-03-23|accessdate=2019-05-06|publisher=Sankei Shimbun}}</ref>\n* ''Nogizaka Doko e'' (NTV, 2019-2020)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ntv.co.jp/program/detail/21882389.html|title= \u3010\u65b0\u3011\u4e43\u6728\u5742\u3069\u3053\u3078\uff5c\u756a\u7d44\u8868\uff5c\u65e5\u672c\u30c6\u30ec\u30d3|accessdate=2019-10-15|publisher=Nippon Television Network Corporation}}</ref>\n* ''Samu no Koto'' (DTV, 2020)\n* ''Saru ni au'' (DTV, 2020)\n\n===Theater===\n* ''16 nin no Principal'' (Shibuya Parco Theater, 2012)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/news/76365|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u521d\u5287\u5834\u516c\u6f14\u306f\u8a66\u7df4\u306e\u9023\u7d9a\u3001\u751f\u7530\uff06\u751f\u99d2\u304c\u672c\u97f3\u8a9e\u308b|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''16 nin no Principal deux'' ([[Akasaka ACT Theater]] and [[Umeda Arts Theater]], 2013)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/news/91944|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u300c16\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb deux\u300d\u5927\u962a\u3067\u611f\u6d99\u306e\u5343\u79cb\u697d|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''16 nin no Principal trois'' (Akasaka ACT Theater, 2014)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/pp/nogizaka46_10|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u300c16\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb trois\u300d\u7279\u96c6 (1/4)|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''[[Joshiraku]]'' (AiiA 2.5 Theater Tokyo, 2015)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2050832/full/|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u3001\u821e\u53f0\u7248\u300e\u3058\u3087\u3057\u3089\u304f\u300f\u3067\u8