er=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''16 nin no Principal deux'' ([[Akasaka ACT Theater]] and [[Umeda Arts Theater]], 2013)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/news/91944|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u300c16\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb deux\u300d\u5927\u962a\u3067\u611f\u6d99\u306e\u5343\u79cb\u697d|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''16 nin no Principal trois'' (Akasaka ACT Theater, 2014)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/pp/nogizaka46_10|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u300c16\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb trois\u300d\u7279\u96c6 (1/4)|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''[[Joshiraku]]'' (AiiA 2.5 Theater Tokyo, 2015)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2050832/full/|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u3001\u821e\u53f0\u7248\u300e\u3058\u3087\u3057\u3089\u304f\u300f\u3067\u843d\u8a9e\u306b\u6311\u6226|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=oricon ME inc.|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''Subete no Inu wa Tengoku e Iku'' (AiiA 2.5 Theater Tokyo, 2015)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2060076/full/|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u5742\u30fb\u677e\u6751\u6c99\u53cb\u7406\u3001\u685c\u4e95\u73b2\u9999\u3068\u30e9\u30d6\u30b7\u30fc\u30f3\u300c\u8272\u6c17\u304c\u958b\u653e\u300d|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=oricon ME inc.|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''Joshiraku 2: Toki Kakesoba'' (AiiA 2.5 Theater Tokyo, 2016)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2071525/full/|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u5742\u30fb\u751f\u99d2\u91cc\u5948\u3001\u6b05\u5742\u4eba\u6c17\u306b\u9a5a\u304d\u300c\u3042\u3084\u304b\u308a\u305f\u3044\u300d |accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=oricon ME inc.|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''Hakaba Joshik\u014dsei'' ([[Tokyo Dome City]] Theater G-Rosso, 2016)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/stage/news/199424|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u5742\u30e1\u30f3\u30d0\u30fc\u304c\u7269\u6182\u3052\u306a\u8868\u60c5\u6d6e\u304b\u3079\u308b\u300c\u5893\u5834\u3001\u5973\u5b50\u9ad8\u751f\u300d\u30d3\u30b8\u30e5\u30a2\u30eb|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''3 nin no Principal'' (3rd Generation members) (AiiA 2.5 Theater Tokyo, 2017)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sp.natalie.mu/music/news/212781|script-title=ja:\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u306e3\u671f\u751f\u304c\u6b66\u9053\u9928\u3067\u500b\u6027\u30a2\u30d4\u30fc\u30eb\u3001\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb\u516c\u6f14\u306e\u958b\u50ac\u3082\u6c7a\u5b9a|date=2016-12-11|accessdate=2017-01-28|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''[[Asahinagu]]'' (Ex Theater Roppongi, 2017)<ref name=\"natasha20170225\">{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/comic/news/221735|script-title=ja:\u300c\u3042\u3055\u3072\u306a\u3050\u300d\u897f\u91ce\u4e03\u702c\u3067\u6620\u753b\u5316\uff06\u9f4b\u85e4\u98db\u9ce5\u3067\u821e\u53f0\u5316\u6c7a\u5b9a\u3001\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u3068\u30bf\u30c3\u30b0|date=2017-02-22|accessdate=2017-02-25|publisher=Natasha,Inc|language=ja}}</ref>\n* ''3 nin no Principal'' (4th Generation members) (Sunshine Theater, 2019)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nogizaka46.com/smph/news/2019/03/464-3.php|title=\u4e43\u6728\u574246\u30004\u671f\u751f\u521d\u516c\u6f14 \u300c\uff13\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ea\u30f3\u30b7\u30d1\u30eb\u300d\u958b\u50ac\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff06\u30e2\u30d0\u30a4\u30eb\u5148\u884c\u958b\u59cb\uff01|date=2019-03-27|accessdate=2019-04-25|publisher=Nogizaka46 Official Website|language=ja}}</ref>\n\n== Awards ==\nThe following table lists some of the major awards received by the group.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Ceremony\n! Award\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n|-\n|2013\n| Japan Gold Disc Awards<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.golddisc.jp/award/27/index.html#gd27_02|title=Japan Gold Disc Awards 2013}}</ref>\n| New Artist of the Year\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2015\n| Japan Gold Disc Awards<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.golddisc.jp/award/29/Prize_2.html#gd29_20|title=29th Japan Gold Disc Awards}